                    Review Date: 2026-02-02
================================================================================


================================================================================
EXECUTIVE SUMMARY
================================================================================

Prospect is a premium Webflow template designed for B2B SaaS and fintech
applications. It features a sophisticated dark-mode aesthetic, multiple page
variations for A/B testing, and a component system optimized for conversion.

Key Strengths:
- Multiple homepage/feature/about variations for testing
- Strong social proof integration throughout
- Problem-solution narrative structure
- Clean visual hierarchy with generous whitespace
- Professional photography over stock illustrations


================================================================================
LAYOUT ANALYSIS
================================================================================

GRID SYSTEM
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
┌────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│     Property       │                    Specification                       │
├────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Breakpoints        │ Desktop: 992px+                                        │
│                    │ Tablet: 768-991px                                      │
│                    │ Mobile Large: 480-767px                                │
│                    │ Mobile Small: <480px                                   │
├────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Container          │ Centered, max-width constrained                        │
│                    │ Full-bleed sections for hero/feature blocks            │
├────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Column Grid        │ Flexible (2-col, 3-col, 4-col layouts observed)        │
│                    │ Cards use equal-width distribution                     │
├────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Spacing            │ Generous vertical padding between sections             │
│                    │ Consistent internal padding on cards                   │
└────────────────────┴────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘


