ABOVE-THE-FOLD STRATEGY
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                                                                             │
│   Priority 1: Value proposition headline (what you get)                     │
│   Priority 2: Benefit statement (why it matters)                            │
│   Priority 3: Dual CTAs (action options)                                    │
│   Priority 4: Social proof (trust signals)                                  │
│   Priority 5: Product imagery/dashboard preview                             │
│                                                                             │
│   Pattern: Everything needed to decide "should I explore?" appears          │
│   within first viewport. No scrolling required for basic understanding.     │
│                                                                             │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘


