CARD HOVER EFFECTS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Cards appear to use subtle elevation or shadow changes on hover.
The template emphasizes "smooth, intentional motion rather than
aggressive animations" per analysis.


SCROLL ANIMATIONS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
┌────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│     Property       │                    Specification                       │
├────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Pattern            │ Fade-in + translate on scroll into view                │
├────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Desktop translate  │ 72px downward (starts 72px above, animates to 0)       │
├────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Mobile translate   │ 48px downward                                          │
├────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Opacity            │ Starts at 0, animates to 1                             │
├────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Stagger            │ Elements animate in sequence (staggered timing)        │
└────────────────────┴────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘


FORM INTERACTIONS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Form fields have visible focus states (likely border color change)
- Success message: "Thank you! Your submission has been received!"
- Error messaging for validation failures
- Checkbox with terms agreement before submission


ACCORDION/FAQ BEHAVIOR
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Expandable sections for FAQ content
- Click to toggle open/closed
- 7-9 questions typically displayed
- Categories may be grouped


