================================================================================
DIFFERENCES FROM ADVYSER CONTEXT
================================================================================

Prospect is B2B SaaS selling to finance teams.
Advyser is a B2C marketplace connecting consumers with financial advisors.

ADAPTATIONS NEEDED
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. TRUST SIGNALS
   Prospect: "500+ companies" (B2B credibility)
   Advyser: "Licensed advisors" (regulatory credibility)
   → Emphasize AFSL verification, ASIC compliance

2. TESTIMONIALS
   Prospect: Business outcomes (time saved, efficiency)
   Advyser: Life outcomes (retirement confidence, debt freedom)
   → Focus on emotional transformation, not operational metrics

3. PRICING
   Prospect: Clear tiers for subscription product
   Advyser: Free for consumers, advisor-side monetization
   → Pricing page becomes "For Advisors" with lead credits/subscription

4. HERO IMAGERY
   Prospect: Dashboard screenshots, product interfaces
   Advyser: People meeting advisors, diverse Australians planning futures
   → Human connection over software screenshots


